<plot>This documentary treats movie fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Superman II, in which a gang of criminals from Superman's home planet arrive on Earth to begin terrorizing the Man of Steel's adopted home. Included are interviews with the cast and crew who share their experiences from making the film, as well as disscuss the efforts that went into it.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?574100</url></doc>
